high_descs: Turn right and walk around the room to face the fridge on the left.
Take the tomato out of the fridge.
Turn right and follow the counter to the end and turn left to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn left and follow the counter to the end and turn right to face the fridge.
Put the tomato back in it's original spot in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a tomato and put it back in it's spot in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the tomato out of the fridge, then close the fridge door.
Turn around and walk over to the kitchen island, then turn left and walk up to the counter, turn right and walk over to the microwave.
Put the tomato in the microwave to the right of the egg and microwave it for a couple seconds, then take it out and close the microwave door.
Turn left and walk over to the stove, then walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the heated tomato inside.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato in the fridge.

high_descs: pick the tomato from the fridge
cook the tomato inside the oven and take it out
place the cooked tomato inside the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a cooked tomato inside the fridge
